; Coverage for filters.cc lines 1070-1071:
; interval_posts::operator() when interval has no duration.
; Using --period with only a date range (no weekly/monthly) triggers
; the find_period path without a duration.

2024/01/01 First
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/01 Second
    Expenses:Food    $20.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/03/01 Third
    Expenses:Food    $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --period "from 2024/01/15 to 2024/02/15"
24-Feb-01 Second                Expenses:Food                $20.00       $20.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-20.00            0
end test
